com.opengamma.strata.examples.marketdata.credit.markit

Enum MarkitRestructuringClause

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MarkitRestructuringClause>
      • com.opengamma.strata.examples.marketdata.credit.markit.MarkitRestructuringClause
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MarkitRestructuringClause>

    public enum MarkitRestructuringClause
extends Enum<MarkitRestructuringClause>
    Specifies the form of the restructuring credit event that is applicable to the credit default swap.

    This is also known as the DocClause.
